{"tid":1980752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【向消防員方sir送暖】","createTime":"2020-04-20T09:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T09:46:46.000Z","uid":289020,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"477361c859751d9ed521329a11440f19c463c360","tid":1980752,"uid":289020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:22:59.000Z","msg":"Source: 星火同盟 抗爭支援<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1965117443775378/posts/2741941382759643/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1965117443775378%2Fposts%2F2741941382759643%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=f0cebf76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1965117443775378/posts/2741941382759643/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【向消防員方sir送暖】<br />\n<br />\n去年連串反送中行動中，於11月在旺角衝突中不幸被捕的消防員方志雄(方sir)，最近被控方修改其控罪為一項管有物品意圖摧毁財產罪、一項拒捕罪及一項管有違禁武器罪，另加一項非法集結罪共四項控罪。他早前申請保釋被拒，目前已被還押近半年。<br />\n<br />\n方sir曾參與2017年颱風襲港時在飛鵝山的營救行動，並獲發為消防員最高榮耀的嘉許，足證他守護香港愛護市民之心，惜這次不幸被迫害而遭受還押。<br />\n<br />\n失去自由這五個多月，方sir 的妻子為他誕下孩子，為人父的他因此從未能擁抱自己的孩子，初生小寶寶失去父親疼愛的機會，據報太太亦患上產後抑鬱症。<br />\n<br />\n本平台收到許多同道對方sir的關心和問候，在取得他的同意下，現幫助收集大家的心意卡和信件。<br />\n<br />\n同道們即日起可留言、私訊或將心意卡和信件寄到本平台信箱：尖沙咀郵箱98697號。我們會將大家的關心和問候，一一轉交到方sir手中，希望能讓他知道，很多市民仍不住的關心和惦記他及他的一家。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎仍然在全球肆虐，本平台深盼各位同道忙於抗疫的同時，能夠抽空將關心方sir的心意轉化成訊息或信件，讓我們送到他手中。同道們給予方sir的每一個鼓勵和打氣，將成為他面對四面圍牆時重要的精神支柱。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XYZFV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XYZFV4.jpg&h=60844911&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30f08069ccace32dd5c47b6333d6415a5a0becbb","tid":1980752,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:24:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0dbf41f163289b62a60fb9a5ce5cc7ce084b4fda","tid":1980752,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:24:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83309297ce9e8548fb5ef0d492b017a9dc85ccd7","tid":1980752,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8747176e226aa0331d313e82e3a6bef55844e939","tid":1980752,"uid":317378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:24:50.000Z","msg":"會唔會有第二輪夾錢買玩具車，第一輪跟唔倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ea5a68b8a48d323fd2d6001eed085b8246ee9a","tid":1980752,"uid":289020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c004349f4bc53ec0e78e95a7e73b2487277c0cb4","tid":1980752,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff9ec4ca74843fcb5718a9f9522a66e8c19edae","tid":1980752,"uid":289020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8747176e226aa0331d313e82e3a6bef55844e939","tid":1980752,"uid":317378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:24:50.000Z","msg":"會唔會有第二輪夾錢買玩具車，第一輪跟唔倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:25:55.000Z","msg":"唔知呀 而家淨係知有得寫信"},{"pid":"f10d48f8b88431d209f76588c3399ebaec803208","tid":1980752,"uid":81533,"like":0,"dislike